<td>↑</td>
<td style="text-align:left">&#160;&#8226;&#32;Decreased <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sensitization" title="Sensitization">sensitivity</a> to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glutamate" class="mw-redirect" title="Glutamate">glutamate</a></td>
