<li id="cite_note-14"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Drug_addiction#cite_ref-14">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFHenden2017" class="citation book">Henden E (2017). "Addiction, Compulsion, and Weakness of the Will: A Dual-Process Perspective.".  In Heather N, Gabriel S (eds.). <i>Addiction and Choice: Rethinking the Relationship</i>. Oxford, UK: Oxford University Press. pp.&#160;116–132.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Addiction%2C+Compulsion%2C+and+Weakness+of+the+Will%3A+A+Dual-Process+Perspective.&amp;rft.btitle=Addiction+and+Choice%3A+Rethinking+the+Relationship&amp;rft.place=Oxford%2C+UK&amp;rft.pages=116-132&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2017&amp;rft.aulast=Henden&amp;rft.aufirst=Edmund&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAddiction" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
