<li id="cite_note-42"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Drug_addiction#cite_ref-42">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFHallDrgonovaJainUhl2013" class="citation journal">Hall FS, Drgonova J, Jain S, Uhl GR (December 2013). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3797854">"Implications of genome wide association studies for addiction: are our a priori assumptions all wrong?"</a>. <i>Pharmacology &amp; Therapeutics</i>. <b>140</b> (3): 267–79. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1016%2Fj.pharmthera.2013.07.006">10.1016/j.pharmthera.2013.07.006</a>. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PMC_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMC (identifier)">PMC</a>&#160;<span class="cs1-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3797854">3797854</a></span>. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PMID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMID (identifier)">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23872493">23872493</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Pharmacology+%26+Therapeutics&amp;rft.atitle=Implications+of+genome+wide+association+studies+for+addiction%3A+are+our+a+priori+assumptions+all+wrong%3F&amp;rft.volume=140&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=267-79&amp;rft.date=2013-12&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3797854&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F23872493&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1016%2Fj.pharmthera.2013.07.006&amp;rft.aulast=Hall&amp;rft.aufirst=FS&amp;rft.au=Drgonova%2C+J&amp;rft.au=Jain%2C+S&amp;rft.au=Uhl%2C+GR&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3797854&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2