</li>
<li id="cite_note-Nestler,_Hyman,_and_Malenka_2-73"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="Drug_addiction#cite_ref-Nestler,_Hyman,_and_Malenka_2_73-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="Drug_addiction#cite_ref-Nestler,_Hyman,_and_Malenka_2_73-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFHymanMalenkaNestler2006" class="citation journal">Hyman SE, Malenka RC, Nestler EJ (2006). "Neural mechanisms of addiction: the role of reward-related learning and memory". <i>Annu. Rev. Neurosci</i>. <b>29</b>: 565–98. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1146%2Fannurev.neuro.29.051605.113009">10.1146/annurev.neuro.29.051605.113009</a>. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PMID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMID (identifier)">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16776597">16776597</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Annu.+Rev.+Neurosci.&amp;rft.atitle=Neural+mechanisms+of+addiction%3A+the+role+of+reward-related+learning+and+memory&amp;rft.volume=29&amp;rft.pages=565-98&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1146%2Fannurev.neuro.29.051605.113009&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F16776597&amp;rft.aulast=Hyman&amp;rft.aufirst=SE&amp;rft.au=Malenka%2C+RC&amp;rft.au=Nestler%2C+EJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAddiction" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
